    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Luxury Sport Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior features a deep midnight blue metallic finish that still holds a brilliant shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest highway miles. Inside, you\u2019ll find premium perforated leather seats that have been regularly conditioned, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the panoramic sunroof and the premium 12-speaker sound system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the turbocharged engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history at authorized dealerships. We recently fitted a fresh set of all-season performance tires and performed a full fluid flush. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a refined driving experience that remains spirited and dependable. It is a complete package for anyone seeking luxury without the brand-new price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
